text: Gunta Lamaša (born 29 February 1972) is a Latvian rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Latvian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Latvia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Riga
